data.description: Amazing brick ranch home in Broad Bay Point Greens in the Great Neck corridor of Virginia Beach with Lake and Golf course views. This home overlooks the 9th hole, beautiful landscaping with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 baths on a cul de sac. As you enter the home you have a separate living and dining rooms with stunning wood flooring. Huge kitchen with breakfast area, nice cabinets with undermount lighting, granite counter tops, center isle with hanging pot rack and copper pots and stainless-steel appliances. The family room has a cathedral ceiling, built-ins and fireplace. The spacious primary room and bath have a large walk-in closet, separate shower, jetted tub and dual sink vanities. Bedroom over the garage has its own full bath. Large laundry room. Huge deck to relax or entertain friends and family with water garden/pond. New outside HVAC and water heater. Broad Bay Country Club and pool membership available. Close to beaches, restaurants, shopping, military bases, interstates bay and more!
